title: DiskGenius Professional 4.9.6.564 Full With Medicine[BabuPC]
description:
Pro helps you restore files that are deleted by mistake, lost without reason, partition reformatted, system crashes, virus attack, partition failure…; Recovering lost partitions by rebuilding MBR, rebuilding partition table; and what’s more it is a useful tool to manage disk partitions and it can backup partitions.

As a one tool but fixes various disk problems including file missing, partition lost, bad MBR, partition table errors… it also enables you to ensure your disk safety by creating an image file of your partition and its files as a backup.
Highlights of DiskGenius

    Windows 7 & Dos supported
    Diskgenius supports most Windows plantform including Windows 7, Vista, XP, Server 2000-2008. Dos version is provided.
    Recover files
    Recovering files from deletion, partition deleted, partition formatted, bad mbr, bad partition table, system crashes, software wrong operations like resizing partition size failure, ghost failure…
    Rebuild MBR | Rebuild Partition Table 
    Diskgenius is able to rebuild MBR and partition table to restore lost partitions and fix system errors.
    Check Partition Errors
    This tool is able to check partition errors to make sure your disk partitions are well.
    Recover delete partitions
    Recovering deleted, lost partitions in a few seconds.
    Disk Management
    Format disk and create partitions when first bought your disk; set partition between active and inactive, primary and logical
